I figured the option of %T>% to create variables mid pipe in #rstats then use later:

library(dplyr)
library(magrittr)

xmple <- data.frame(a=1:10,b=21:30)

create_var_1 <- function(x){
  y=mean(x[,1])
  var_1 <<- y}

xmple %T>%
  create_var_1 %>% 
  filter(a > var_1, b > var_1)
